{"tid":404544,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[組 隊] 想 搵 一 班 對 調 酒 有 興 趣 既 人","createTime":"2017-09-18T07:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T17:12:48.000Z","uid":106326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecbe73c189bebc08449a1692c992ee2c6d6f881","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"小弟曾經因興趣而入行做過一段時間。<br />\n無做之後同朋友夾份租studio既時候亦預留左一部份黎setup 個bar，設備尚算齊全，但一個人玩又有D悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n現在想搵對調酒有認識既人組個同好會，無論你係同行，還是飲方面都好有認識都可以，我地一齊去研究點樣先可以令杯酒更好飲，甚至可以做下實驗，用你未諗過既食材整cocktail也好。<br />\n<br />\n材料器具上面都有了，如果成功組隊的話，希望大家係玩既同時，可以多少夾份材料費。<br />\n<br />\n未知有冇人有興趣，過往係高/連登開既調酒POST都係好快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以睇完反應 之後再決定點聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9a0a573298b75bb50b4522c2c1da7e616a8884","tid":404544,"uid":140189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚮邊度先？<br />\n屋企真係擺唔到咁多野"},{"pid":"adb1ebc9528e8674cf91f6aaa7959dd9a133bc72","tid":404544,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"鐘意飲 但唔識 想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4745a769aada4cbe03334334f37e97e6d78c8998","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚮邊度先？<br />\n屋企真係擺唔到咁多野</blockquote><br />\n我放係屋企比老母剷上天花板"},{"pid":"578ab63c52d42e47b72dc32ff2ae632b31dbc43c","tid":404544,"uid":140189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚮邊度先？<br />\n屋企真係擺唔到咁多野</blockquote><br />\n我放係屋企比老母剷上天花板</blockquote><br />\n我都係得幾支spirit同liqueur<br />\n教我切garnish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申揸刀白痴"},{"pid":"a4deb17ce9fda32c439ad2939b55cb5772cb38cd","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"已沉"},{"pid":"edb7040e9669d43618fe9a4ccec4ec35e8956a2c","tid":404544,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00c3952227e9088a0dfb9805a8090f2ffad44e68","tid":404544,"uid":70518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"我係全職bartender<br />\n自己都有個bar仔響朋友鋪頭到<br />\n得閒可以一齊玩"},{"pid":"d0bc270bcaf1adc8f4e65781f4eed587435842cb","tid":404544,"uid":78432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"乜都唔識<br />\n淨係飲過下cocktail同威士忌<br />\n淘左堆裝備想試想學但又無從入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f81f600686d8a396425e7e0c783127d4bde88fb","tid":404544,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:23:35.000Z","msg":"想學，但一直係酒吧都係做緊part time侍應，好少入bar做，學極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地點邊度？"},{"pid":"d721f2fa04935ef786b777c37017dd5c37101b0d","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係全職bartender<br />\n自己都有個bar仔響朋友鋪頭到<br />\n得閒可以一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n熊貓哥不要踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be29a12a71d7dccd30cc0e0d7902330de50d71c","tid":404544,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80a327adf8edd517263ba2a57b72605681f9545","tid":404544,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/184806_4fd87f900b614c77acc8971307416250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F184806_4fd87f900b614c77acc8971307416250.jpg&h=fc88f551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係自己上網學<br />\n酒嘅種類真係買極都買唔曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係試過整d 比較簡單傳統既cocktail<br />\n因為每次想試新嘢買料真係極麻煩<br />\n所以最後放棄左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad46ae44cd967348b6f59fb0ad5e96835ec4392","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/184806_4fd87f900b614c77acc8971307416250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F184806_4fd87f900b614c77acc8971307416250.jpg&h=fc88f551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係自己上網學<br />\n酒嘅種類真係買極都買唔曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係試過整d 比較簡單傳統既cocktail<br />\n因為每次想試新嘢買料真係極麻煩<br />\n所以最後放棄左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夾錢買最好。<br />\n有啲酒真係一世都用唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbece6e37a4c07bbabba2d6da3992351af3b81da","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"無人黎，我都拋磚引玉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人有興趣一齊研究呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/201942_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F201942_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1631f771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/201946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F201946_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=008db977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/201949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F201949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d800dcdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97f786e556b4d03882c83584dfb64e5864878bdc","tid":404544,"uid":70518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/184806_4fd87f900b614c77acc8971307416250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F184806_4fd87f900b614c77acc8971307416250.jpg&h=fc88f551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係自己上網學<br />\n酒嘅種類真係買極都買唔曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係試過整d 比較簡單傳統既cocktail<br />\n因為每次想試新嘢買料真係極麻煩<br />\n所以最後放棄左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好晒錢買杯啦<br />\n如果真係怕用唔晒...拎個100~200ml既樽問巴打買/問我拎<br />\n或者i x cake都有細細樽for甜品用"},{"pid":"2d5d70d30dd52435c99a05772eac99bdd535493b","tid":404544,"uid":34264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"有興趣 冇時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"b4099478c1a17e9a6c29d01f19ce7d8a9e75a268","tid":404544,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"之前行啲鋪頭見到有啲杯 一套六隻 每隻杯都刻左啲cocktails 啲溝 有晒刻度好似幾正 但都成兩舊水一套"},{"pid":"f25063b3864edd2973fdae5afc80ab0401f6eaa2","tid":404544,"uid":70518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前行啲鋪頭見到有啲杯 一套六隻 每隻杯都刻左啲cocktails 啲溝 有晒刻度好似幾正 但都成兩舊水一套</blockquote><br />\n千奇唔好買<br />\n跟本唔值"},{"pid":"ae882b01aa655cca372101e73fda89ed785d29ca","tid":404544,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前行啲鋪頭見到有啲杯 一套六隻 每隻杯都刻左啲cocktails 啲溝 有晒刻度好似幾正 但都成兩舊水一套</blockquote><br />\n千奇唔好買<br />\n跟本唔值</blockquote><br />\n咁有無啲類似推介 新手唔識份量好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a374462b10c8e178ff6db35d48336138a96417ad","tid":404544,"uid":16661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"點入行 想試下做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9195772f103a93f35e1abdfc26ac782b3dcf7b","tid":404544,"uid":142663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意飲 但唔識 想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"641a333acd9343acf5d694c4c9b8320f993db5c9","tid":404544,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"dewars<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e161403d1c4fb83416e440fc0fd5b3f4c02fd955","tid":404544,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"有興趣 大概咩地方 預幾錢到？ <br />\n制冰設備？"},{"pid":"42f0a6b9c650f4261dde97a4ce2e90bc9d6a6944","tid":404544,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有興趣 大概咩地方 預幾錢到？ <br />\n制冰設備？</blockquote><br />\n葵興，冰自己雪自己切<br />\n錢睇大家玩幾多"}]}